CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1772478695
OL,3,CYoung musicians plant trees to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 100 years of countryside
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FA crowdfunder has been set up to fund
OL,8,Fthe project, aiming to raise #10,000,
OL,9,Fwhich will also see ten kilometres of
OL,10,Fhedgerows planted by next spring.
OL,12,FSarah Pitt, Chair of CPRE Avon &
OL,13,FBristol, said: "This crowdfunder
OL,14,Finvites people to be part of something
OL,15,Ftruly lasting - a project rooted in
OL,16,Fcommunity and grounded in our shared
OL,17,Flove for the countryside.
OL,26,@uD@POU
