PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1772478695
OL,3,CYoung musicians plant trees to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 100 years of countryside
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FThe new centenary woodland made up of
OL,8,Fnative trees including hazel,
OL,9,Fhawthorn, wild pear, bird cherry and
OL,10,Frowan was planted by musicians,
OL,11,Fvolunteers and youngsters from the
OL,12,FBristol charity Babbassa.
OL,14,FIt's accessible to the public and will
OL,15,Fgrow a few hundred metres from the
OL,16,Fhistoric Publow Oak.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
