PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1772478695
OL,3,CYoung musicians plant trees to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 100 years of countryside
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FTim Harrison, Musical Director of
OL,8,FBristol Youth Orchestra, said: "Our
OL,9,Fplayers are not only learning and
OL,10,Fperforming some of the most beautiful
OL,11,Fand evocative music written about the
OL,12,FEnglish landscape - they're also
OL,13,Fstepping into that landscape to
OL,14,Fprotect and renew it. That connection
OL,15,Fgives their performance an even deeper
OL,16,Fsense of purpose."
OL,18,FThe concert will take place on 29th
OL,19,FMarch at the Bristol Beacon.
OL,26,@pD@`OUxD@RO]
